502
00:38:16,199 --> 00:38:19,759
So you and Bas can tutor us in Chinese.

503
00:38:19,759 --> 00:38:21,693
- Sure.
- Okay?

504
00:38:22,180 --> 00:38:23,713
Okay?

505
00:38:24,380 --> 00:38:27,079
Bas, why are you so good at Chinese?

506
00:38:27,079 --> 00:38:30,480
