534
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,679
Calm down.

535
00:40:14,680 --> 00:40:16,679
So you'll have a better score.

536
00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:18,230
My score is my business.

537
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:23,820
